      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by to check out my pride and joy. Honestly, it breaks my heart a little to let this beauty go, but it's time for her to find a new home where she'll be just as pampered. This car is an absolute dream\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied this one since day one, always kept her tucked away in the garage and stayed ahead of every single service. It's truly a 'get in and go' kind of find, perfect for someone who appreciates the finer details. You won't find another one this clean in the neighborhood, I promise! Let's get you behind the wheel for a look.",
